net.sf.appia.core.events.channel
Class ChannelEvent

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.appia.core.Event
      net.sf.appia.core.events.channel.ChannelEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChannelClose, ChannelInit, Debug, EchoEvent, ExternalEvent, PeriodicTimer, Timer
public class ChannelEvent
extends Event

Superclass of all Events accepted by the Channel.
All subclasses of ChannelEvent are handled by the Channel through the handle(Event) method.
A few of the subclasses are also provided by the Channel, namely: ChannelInit, ChannelClose.
A ChannelEvent extends an Event by adding an EventQualifier.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Alexandre Pinto
See Also:
net.sf.appia.core.events.channel, EventQualifier
